responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "98F602AB44581BF57F109DB476B67AB9", "Come and dance two sisters of Sephillion. Dance the dance and wish for me. Tarys, my little spark, what wonders do you wish to see? Tomorrows sun and a thousand more! I wish to see them all. As I do not age like years before.")
